reviewText: Such crazy creative skating!  It might destroy your mind!!
Awesome skills a must watch !!!! Definantly a keeper ...
This Movie is like no other skateboard video you have seen. Very creative tricks. The passion for skateboarding is apparent between Dan and his team.

Dan and his team at Mentality Skateboards have put together a mesmerising video of pure creative awesomeness! Trick after trick after trick, it never gets old because these are unique tricks you definitely haven't seen anywhere else before. Skateboarding Realms takes skateboarding to a whole new untouched level of creative ingenuity! Its so innovative and refreshing, you have to see it to believe it!

This movie is a testament to the creativity of skateboarding and the athletes in it are just world class and truly showing that anyone who puts in the work can skateboard with only the sky being the limit!  In other words "Rad"
